; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; transition: color 0.3s ease 0s; touch-action: manipulation;">完整组件列表</a></p><h2 id="兼容性" style="margin-top: 1.6em; margin-bottom: 0.6em; color: rgb(13, 26, 38); font-weight: 500; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px; font-family: Avenir, &quot;Chinese Quote&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; font-variant-east-asian: normal; clear: both; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">兼容性&nbsp;<a href="https://vue.ant.design/docs/vue/getting-started-cn/#%E5%85%BC%E5%AE%B9%E6%80%A7" aria-hidden="true" style="color: rgb(24, 144, 255); background-color: transparent; text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; transition: opacity 0.3s ease 0s; touch-action: manipulation; opacity: 0; margin-left: 8px;">#</a></h2><p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; color: rgb(49, 70, 89); font-family: &quot;Chinese Quote&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Ant Design Vue 支持所有的现代浏览器和 IE9+。</p><p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; color: rgb(49, 70, 89); font-family: &quot;Chinese Quote&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">对于 IE 系列浏览器，需要提供&nbsp;<a href="https://github.com/es-shims/es5-shim" style="color: rgb(24, 144, 255); background-color: transparent; text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; transition: color 0.3s ease 0s; touch-action: manipulation;">es5-shim</a>&nbsp;和&nbsp;<a href="https://github.com/paulmillr/es6-shim" style="color: rgb(24, 144, 255); background-color: transparent; text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; transition: color 0.3s ease 0s; touch-action: manipulation;">es6-shim</a>&nbsp;等 Polyfills 的支持。</p><p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; color: rgb(49, 70, 89); font-family: &quot;Chinese Quote&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">如果你使用了 babel，强烈推荐使用&nbsp;<a href="https://babeljs.io/docs/usage/polyfill/" style="color: rgb(24, 144, 255); background-color: transparent; text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; transition: color 0.3s ease 0s; touch-action: manipulation;">babel-polyfill</a>&nbsp;和&nbsp;<a href="https://babeljs.io/docs/plugins/transform-runtime/" style="color: rgb(24, 144, 255); background-color: transparent; text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; transition: color 0.3s ease 0s; touch-action: manipulation;">babel-plugin-transform-runtime</a>&nbsp;来替代以上两个 shim。</p><blockquote style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.8em; font-size: 12.6px; color: rgb(105, 123, 140); border-left-width: 4px; border-left-color: rgb(235, 237, 240); font-family: &quot;Chinese Quote&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe 